commit.message: Make it work on Ruby 2.7 up to 3.3
Fix test files to work with newer Minitest versions

Require date library to avoid problems loading the cache file

Sometimes Date objects are in the cache, e.g. when the created_at meta
information is set to 2010-01-10. This *seems* to depend on the actually
used Ruby version and on the actually loaded libraries.

Since webgen doesn't require the date library anywhere, there is an
error when loading the cache due to the missing class Date.

Fix this by loading the date library.
Make content_processor.erb work with older ERB versions
Fix problem with hashing on Ruby 3.0
Use URI.open instead of open for Ruby > 2.5 for source.tar_archive
Fix test cases due to frozen true.to_s
Fix LanguageManager to only use the data after __END__
Update haml to a newer version
Fix path handler API to work with newer RDoc versions
Fix deprecated use of content processor ERB

Structure fragment nodes in path handler API

The fragment nodes for constants, attributes, class methods and instance
methods are now hierarchically structured and within each category
sorted. This makes displaying a table of contents on an API page much
easier.
Create fragment nodes for constants in path handler API
Test for correct creation of fragment nodes for attributes in path handler API
